Package: miicsem
Title: Simulation Framework for MI-AIC/MI-BIC Evaluation in SEM
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Marcus R.",
                  family = "Waldman",
                  email = "marcus.waldman@cuanschutz.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Runs the Bollen et al. (2014) SIM1 SEM simulation to evaluate
    MI-AIC and MI-BIC information criteria against AICcd and ad hoc
    alternatives under missing data with multiple imputation. Designed
    for execution on high-performance computing environments.
